  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ClassResourceNotFoundException
    This is a more specific version of FileNotFoundException for resources available via Class.getResourceAsStream(String).
    InvalidExitValueException
    Thrown by class Process2 if the child process exit value is unexpected.
    PathException
    This is a more specific version of IOException that focuses on path-related errors.
    TimeoutException
    Thrown by class Process2 when waiting for the child process to terminate exceeds the specified time limit.
